===[[Noun]]===

#The first [[day]] of the [[week]]. It is the [[sabbath]] for most [[Christian]]s.  It follows [[Saturday]] and precedes [[Monday]].
#The "venerable day of the sun", as declared by Roman Emperor Constantine on March 7, AD 321.
#The seventh day in systems using the ISO 8601 norm.

